STL TECHNOLOGY C April Sales Fall 19.50% (Table) : 4931 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-05-10T07:38:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/stl-technology-c-april-sales-fall-19-50-table-4931-tt.html
STL TECHNOLOGY C said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 19.50% to NT$569,608,000 from NT$707,552,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            569,608          707,552    
YOY%             -19.50%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,979,536        2,599,159   
YOY%             -23.84% 
=================================================================
 